<pre>
タイトル: <font size = 5>Cerulean　Armor</font>
<b>投稿者　: </b>Miniel＠EM
<!-- ドメイン: 210.238.16.32 -->
URL　　 : 未登録
登録時間:2001年3月30日12時50分</pre>
本文:
<center>
<table width="95%">
<tr bgcolor="#000042"><td>
KaelのRobe売ってるVenderがいるAreaの建物にいるTrainerからStartです。<BR>
<BR>
You say, 'hail Slaggak the Trainer'<BR>
<BR>
Slaggak the Trainer says 'Hello there, Troll. I am Slaggak, the <BR>
trainer.  The Kromrif here will soon be ready to serve the great and <BR>
honorable King Tormax. <BR>
<BR>
You say, 'I will serve'<BR>
Slaggak the Trainer says 'So you say, little one.  Why are you here, <BR>
then?  You should be out slaying those pestering little Coldain or <BR>
maybe those damnable shard wurms and wyverns. <BR>
<BR>
You say, 'what is shard wurms and wyverns?'<BR>
Slaggak the Trainer says 'You must have seen the shard wurms by now!  <BR>
The lizards that roam the lands eating whatever they can find?  They <BR>
can grow to be quite ferocious!  Not nearly as ferocious as their <BR>
ancient cousins, the dragons, but a nuisance nonetheless.  We have a <BR>
bounty on those beasts here in Kael Drakkel. <BR>
<BR>
You say, 'what is bounty?'<BR>
Slaggak the Trainer says 'If you think you have what it takes to slay <BR>
the shard wurms or their relatives, the wyverns, bring back proof of <BR>
your exploits.  For every four shard wurm teeth you bring me, I am <BR>
authorized to reward you with a pair of cerulean greaves.  Every <BR>
fourth ice wyvern stinger will grant you a pair of vambraces. <BR>
<BR>
CSのWyvernからIce Wyvern　Stingerを４本集めて渡します.<BR>
<BR>
Slaggak the Trainer says 'You are truly a worthy little Troll.  I <BR>
hope this armor serves you well.  If it does not, I am sure a <BR>
mercenary such as yourself could find a buyer. <BR>
Your faction standing with Kromrif got better<BR>
Your faction standing with Kromzek got better<BR>
Your faction standing with Coldain got worse<BR>
Your faction standing with ClawsofVeeshan got worse<BR>
You gain experience!!<BR>
<BR>
報酬としてCerulean　Vambraceが貰えます.<BR>
MAGIC　slot:ARM<BR>
AC11 STR2 Wt3.5<BR>
Class:WAR CLR PAL SHD BRD  Race:ALL<BR>
<BR>
見た目緑色っぽいPlateでした。<BR>
GreaveはまだやってないのでLOG同じになるかわかりません…<BR>
<BR>

